Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:24.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧 沉睡心底的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:30.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧 向充滿希望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}無論倒下多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:36.11,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要再次站立起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:42.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是等待 奇跡豈會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:46.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越吧 昨日懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:52.80,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊握住 浮於銀河的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:54.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}不要屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馳騁的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:59.30,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}向著夢想之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:01.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:07.02,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘著這天馬的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:12.86,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 熾熱燃燒的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:18.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信決不屈服的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:26.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 決不停滯決不放棄的勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:33.76,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,0)}直指Ω 奮勇戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.33,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣&galaxy字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當世間面臨邪惡之神的侵略時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便必定會出現奮起迎戰的戰士 聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 年輕聖鬥士們嶄新的傳說即將展開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙在同伴的幫助下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過了由黃金聖鬥士守護的十二宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於站在瑪爾斯面前 與其對峙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加之背叛了父親的伊甸也前來助陣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上地球命運的戰鬥愈發激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距地球被黑暗所籠罩只剩20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙與伊甸！年輕的小宇宙啊 討伐黑暗吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你認為能打倒為父的話 就來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…瑪爾斯就由我來打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的第七感已經覺醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 只憑這個是無法打倒我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的力量就想超越我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這種渺小的憤怒產生的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有當絕望根源於靈魂深處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到撕心裂魄的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心被幾近瘋癲的狂怒所支配之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這狂怒的深淵之中才會孕育出黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這種黑暗 這種狂怒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能成為真正的破壞之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是那種感覺 我也曾經歷過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你對阿莉雅下手的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在失去必須去守護的重要生命時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所感到的那種憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在那時 我理想中的父親也一併消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對不會 繼承你的世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個世界 不是阿莉雅所期待的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅想要保護的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我會竭盡全力來打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這逆子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 如果這是你的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要和你並肩戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去上面吧 天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面有阿莉雅的手杖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅的手杖？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那手杖是將地球的小宇宙引向火星的力量之源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能把那手杖拿回來 地球就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去粉碎瑪爾斯的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 等著我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼要背叛我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:05:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我的兒子啊 伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已不再是你的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你 是我的敵人 瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果阿莉雅的手杖可以成為拯救世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何也要得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我和瑪爾斯大人才能靠近阿莉雅的手杖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片刻之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片刻之後 地球的小宇宙就會開始向火星轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 你剛剛到底說了些什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然說我是敵人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然把自己的親生父親稱為敵人嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然要背叛我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我的仇敵！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了你 只為你一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才決定以阿莉雅的力量創造理想的世界 可你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要破壞那個世界嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的世界 我的一切 甚至我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要將這一切都抹殺嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒…甚至悲傷 都化作了我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:08:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 這是你自找的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星永恆槍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也在阿莉雅的手杖前殞命吧 天馬座光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星烈風暴（Rubel Sidus Storm）！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你只擁有守護星座這一個力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今整個宇宙的黑暗都會成為我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 還能站著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星隕石落（Rubel Sidus Meteor）！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 吾乃軍神瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量超越雅典娜 支配一切之時已經到來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今再無人能夠凌駕於我的小宇宙之上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到來吧 新世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經無能為力了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢 尤娜 蒼摩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰 榮斗 還有大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 我並非獨自前行至此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是依靠大家的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 還能站立起來嗎 天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓舞你戰鬥至此的光之碎片 我看得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 憑那借來的力量又能做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬彗星拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗星拳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 這區區一絲光芒又能奈我何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來親自一嘗自己的拳如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只有一絲 光芒也是光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一縷光芒 也能照亮前方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微弱的光才會綻放出強烈的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一線光明 就能繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的希望之路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要妨礙我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不是我的兒子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻礙我創造新世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰我都不會手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這黑暗中 你們的存在本身也會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敞開心靈 用第七感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓感官更加敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星永恆槍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星隕石落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷電跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星烈風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧 小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬衝過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等強烈的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要看不見瑪爾斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的光芒指引我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光芒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然突破了我的黑暗力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這種程度的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全及不上我的黑暗力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能在這裡倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要阻止瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的 我們一定能打倒瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們心中還有希望的光芒存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有希望打倒瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了 在那黑暗中…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那黑暗中潛伏的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚存於瑪爾斯之中的 父親的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們還有再一次站起來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能打倒瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量 當然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這份力量能打倒瑪爾斯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還想反抗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們只有死路一條
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會只有一次 天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟鳴吧 我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到生命的最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然主動捨棄自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會從您的身邊消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿莉雅一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和姐姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為您兒子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會從您的身邊消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和您失去妻子的時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對您獻出真心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會在黑暗中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是您想要創造的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要創造的是你 你們生活的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妻子死去的世界不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平又安寧的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想創造的…是這樣的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打敗父親！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別錯過這個時機！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀吧 我的小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬彗星拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的黑暗…消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的聖鬥士的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於結束了瑪爾斯的黑暗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的內心一直被黑暗所籠罩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我能看到光明！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我最後的力量拯救地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和阿莉雅直到最後都想要守護的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了 通往新世界的序曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機已經成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙和伊甸終於擊敗了瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻無法阻止地球的崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了奪回阿莉雅的手杖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙和伊甸胸懷最後的希望 前往火星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 暗之力得到增強的阿墨爾擋在了兩人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一線希望！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的戰鬥之地！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
